Package ohos.media.photokit.support

Class FetchResult<Type>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.media.photokit.support.FetchResult<Type>
  • Type Parameters:
    Type - Indicates the type of the instances in the result set.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class FetchResult<Type>
extends Object
implements Closeable
    Represents a result set that contains either AlbumList or AlbumListInfo instances, and provides methods to get an instance at a specified position in the FetchResult instance.
    Since:
    5
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Multimedia#MEDIA_LIBRARY

        public void close​()
        Description copied from interface: Closeable
        Closes this stream and releases any system resources associated with it. If the stream is already closed then invoking this method has no effect.

        As noted in AutoCloseable#close(), cases where the close may fail require careful attention. It is strongly advised to relinquish the underlying resources and to internally mark the Closeable as closed, prior to throwing the IOException.
